      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Scholarly Insights Submission Process"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-814a-b266-c17cd2814b2d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T05:59:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T05:59:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Scholarly Insights is known for their rigorous review process. Authors should prepare for a comprehensive evaluation of their manuscript's contribution to the field. The review can take up to six months, and authors are encouraged to submit their work well in advance of any deadlines they aim to meet."
